{
  "stem": "10353.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A Jew couldn't open up a business, unless-- unless he couldn't employ-- a Jewish corporation couldn't employ Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had to have 96% non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only 6% could-- could be in managerial position-- only 6%.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You were relegated to manual work only.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you lived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And of course, the-- the war scene took a stranglehold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everything was rationed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Jews did not enjoy the same rationing as non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But you went around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You worked around it, and you lived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In May of 19-- 1941, I decided to leave my hometown because Halmeu is a smaller town-- not small, it was about 80,000-- 80,000 to 100,000 inhabitants.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I moved up to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In Budapest--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By myself.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they didn't like it, but they didn't have very much to offer for me in support.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, I was already my 18th year, and so I had to fend for myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had already acquired the knowledge of salesmanship in the textile business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went up to Budapest for better-- to-- to seek something better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You get lost-- in a bigger city, you get lost.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, while anti-Semitism existed, and you knew that existed, but you could sort of mingle more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were great restrictions by that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have eliminated all the Jewish art, like actors and actresses couldn't appear, Jewish actresses couldn't appear, and Jewish music wouldn't be played openly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the Jews organized themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they created their own theaters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As for myself, I-- I couldn't become a salesman, per se, because like I told you, because of the numerus clausus, in this respect-- only 6%.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like for instance, if I want to work in a store, they have to have at least two, three non-Jewish salesmen before I could hold a job.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
